# Design System

## Color Tokens
- Primary: #FF5A5F (Vocoder Red)
- Secondary: #FFE66D (Signal Yellow)
- Accent: #32A8A0 (Wave Teal)
- Background: #0F0F0F (Dark Mode Default)
- Surface: #1C1C1C (Panels & Cards)
- On-Primary: #FFFFFF

## Typography
- Heading Font: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif
- Body Font: "Inter", sans-serif

## Components
- Buttons: Rounded full, bold text, large tap targets
- Cards: 2xl rounded corners, soft drop shadow
- Inputs: Subtle outlines, clear focus state
- Tabs: Underline-style indicator, animated

## Layout
- Grid-based layout
- Responsive down to mobile
- Adequate padding: at least p-2, default to p-4 for cards

## Tailwind Patterns
- Use `text-balance` for large text blocks
- `rounded-2xl` for cards, `rounded-full` for avatars or key UI
- `shadow-md` or `shadow-lg` for elevation
- `transition-all` and `duration-200` on interactive components
